{
  "stem": "1496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I arrived over there, at the railroad station, some people, Polish people, told me, you see, there is a sidetrack from the railroad station into the forest.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The transport are going into-- all the cattle cars with people-- are going into the forest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Empty cattle cars are coming out, and that's all what we can tell you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So far, nobody came out from out there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Later on, much, much later-- even, actually, after the war-- I found out that this was an extermination camp, which was in existence only for one year.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In one year, more than 600,000 Jews were destroyed in this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remained in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My life had to go on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was very difficult at that time, being 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had to cope with my life the best I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I joined with one of my friends, who also lost his family, and he was a very close friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we just stuck together and helped us-- help each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was in the ghetto until liquidation of the Krakow ghetto, what was August 13, 1943.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When the ghetto-- I was during the liquidation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Spielberg tried to show you some of the horror of the liquidation of the Krakow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But actually, I can witness-- I am a witness-- that the liquidation was much worse than actually Spielberg could show you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We are talking about liquidation of the nursery, where all the babies were killed by the SS women, and SS men.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, the complete liquidation by ordering all the people to go on a square, report on the square.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Machine guns were set up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All the people were killed-- a few thousand of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
